<Algorithm code="             1. Let _bindingObject_ be _envRec_.[[BindingObject]].             1. Let _stillExists_ be ? HasProperty(_bindingObject_, _N_).             1. If _stillExists_ is *false* and _S_ is *true*, throw a *ReferenceError* exception.             1. Perform ? Set(_bindingObject_, _N_, _V_, _S_).             1. Return ~unused~.           ">
